casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Vanderhorst, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Vanderhorst, 134 Ohio St.3d 592, 2012-Ohio-5759.]

(No. 2012-1303 Submitted December 4, 2012 Decided December 7, 2012.) William D. Mason, Cuyahoga County Prosecuting Attorney, and Kristen L. Sobieski, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellant. Robert L. Tobik, Cuyahoga County Public Defender, and Nathaniel McDonald, Assistant Public Defender, for appellee.

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on the authority of State v. Williams, 134 Ohio St.3d 482, 2012-Ohio-5699, — N.E.2d-.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, Lanzinger, Cupp, and McGee Brown, JJ., concur. O’Donnell, J., dissents.
